Subject: [PATCH 189/777] drm/i915: Add Wa_1408615072 and Wa_1407596294 to
 icl,ehl

commit a7f3ad37f80d0d5eec9dad156964c0dac800a80e upstream.

Workaround database indicates we should disable clock gating of both the
vsunit and hsunit.

